snippet.textDisplay:
I picked her up from the airport after 2 years of breakup. We had nothing in common anymore. We were two completely different people now. Once who were the beat of the heart of everyone who knew us. We had dreamt everything together of achieving in life. 
This song started playing on radio and we both went silent, since it came out at a time when we were together and loved listening to this song promising never to leave. It’s hilarious how life’s  mysteries are. The last verse of this song of Faisal bhai touched more than it should’ve. 

Kahani kahan, khatam hoti hai. 
Puri nahi, har qasm hoti hai. 
Phir milenge kabhi, “Ajnabi” ki tarha. 
Is aas mein, dil me subah rakhi hai.

 Its been a week since and I haven’t been able to figure out how to feel about all this situation.
